Package: mminer
Type: Package
Title: Marketing Miner Profilers API wrapper in R
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Marek Prokop
Maintainer: Marek Prokop <mprokop@prokopsw.cz>
Description: The mminer package is a simple wrapper for Marketing Miner Profilers API. 
  It fetches search volume data and cache them locally to save credits when necessary.
